0:00: Pour 50g of water off the boil to bloom
0:10 - 0:15: gently swirl
0:00 - 0:45: bloom
0:45 - 1:00: pour 50g of water (100g total)
1:00 - 1:10: pause
1:10 - 1:20: pour 50g of water (150g total)
1:20 - 1:30: pause
1:30 - 1:40: pour 50g of water (200g total)
1:40 - 1:50: pause
1:50 - 2:00: pour 50g of water (250g total)
2:00: gentle swirl
draw down (until about 3:00)
